exceptions.exn: In environment T : Type F : (T -> Prop) -> Prop filter_F : Filter F f, g : T -> R F_cond : F (fun x : T => g x <> 0) domin_F : is_domin F f g eps : posreal Unable to unify "F (fun x : T => g x <> 0)" with "F (fun x : T => norm (/ f x) <= eps * norm (/ g x))".

original: intros T F filter_F f g F_cond domin_F. unfold is_domin. intros eps. apply F_cond.
